what was it?

02:46.400 --> 02:47.699
TIMMY: A monster movie.

02:47.701 --> 02:49.168
Fine, I'll put it back on.

02:56.609 --> 02:57.576
Hey, Miss Witch,
why don't you give
those fingers a rest

02:57.578 --> 02:59.845
and go wash your face.

02:59.847 --> 03:02.681
