1:00? Hopefully sooner.

03:05.719 --> 03:07.486
I get to stay up
till one?

03:07.488 --> 03:09.888
No, bedtime's at 11.

03:09.890 --> 03:11.857
Stop eating all that candy.
You're gonna be up
until tomorrow morning.

03:13.226 --> 03:13.859
SARAH: Very cute.

03:15.528 --> 03:17.529
Your parents
owe me for this one.

03:17.531 --> 03:19.631
You could slap him
if you want.
I won't tell.

03:19.633 --> 03:21.700
Oh, really?
I'll keep that in mind.

03:23.703 --> 03:27.706
What time is it?
Oh, it's 10:50.

03:27.708 --> 03:29.708
All right, seriously,
pumpkin carving
in 10 minutes.

03:29.710 --> 03:31.643
