03:31.645 --> 03:33.712
Yeah, come on, Timmy.
Get the hell up.

03:33.714 --> 03:35.447
I'm not done
counting my candy, loser.

03:36.549 --> 03:38.584
Can we just bury him
in the backyard

03:38.586 --> 03:40.519
