we lost him trick-or-treating?

03:48.795 --> 03:50.429
Hey, look what I got.

03:53.733 --> 03:54.566
What is that?

03:55.802 --> 03:56.702
It's a videotape.

03:57.870 --> 03:59.571
Where did
you get that?

03:59.573 --> 04:00.439
Fell out
of my bag.

04:02.475 --> 04:03.375
Let me see it.

04:06.479 --> 04:07.913
Who gave this to you?
I don't know.

04:09.282 --> 04:10.382
You don't remember
who put it in your bag?

04:10.817 --> 04:11.817
No.

04:19.926 --> 04:21.260
It doesn't say anything.

04:22.762 --> 04:24.463
Let's watch it.
Oh, absolutely not.

04:25.398 --> 04:26.898
Why?

04:26.900 --> 04:29.434
Why? Because God knows
what's on this, that's why.

04:29.436 --> 04:30.435
Only one way
to find out.

04:32.505 --> 04:34.573
Timmy, you're
not watching it.
Yes I am.

04:34.575 --> 04:35.741
Timmy, stop being
such an asshole.

04:36.309 --> 04:39.411
Hey! I said no.

04:39.413 --> 04:41.813
It's my tape, I can do
what I want with it.

04:41.815 --> 04:44.483
Yeah, well, I'm in charge
of you and you have
to listen to me.

04:44.485 --> 04:46.718
Let your parents watch it.
If they say it's okay,
you can watch it tomorrow.

04:46.720 --> 04:47.919
No. I wanna
watch it now.

04:47.921 --> 04:48.987
No, you're
not watching it.

04:50.923 --> 04:52.858
Fine.
Let's put it
to a vote.

04:52.860 --> 04:53.959
I vote
we watch it
right now.

04:55.795 --> 04:57.629
SARAH: Put it to a vote?

04:57.631 --> 04:58.764
What is this?
The town hall?

05:02.902 --> 05:04.503
Little traitor,
now you're on his side?

05:05.972 --> 05:08.540
What? I just wanna see
what's on the tape.

05:08.542 --> 05:11.310
Two against one.
We win, put it on.

05:11.312 --> 05:12.978
Do you understand
this is creepy?

05:12.980 --> 05:14.780
Some pervert
could have put it
in your bag.

05:14.782 --> 05:16.481
Who knows what's on this?

05:16.483 --> 05:18.750
It's probably
just a scary movie.

05:18.752 --> 05:20.886
If it's that bad,
you can turn it off.
We won't tell our parents.

05:22.822 --> 05:25.724
It can't be worse
than the stuff we see
on the Internet every day.

05:25.726 --> 05:28.527
what do you watch
on the Internet?

05:28.529 --> 05:29.761
You know what?
I don't wanna know.

05:30.363 --> 05:31.963
Please.

05:31.965 --> 05:33.465
We won't make you
carve the pumpkin.

05:38.404 --> 05:40.605
