Well, give me a second!

06:18.578 --> 06:19.544
Anything?

06:20.480 --> 06:21.580
I don't see anything.

06:25.985 --> 06:27.119
Looks like you
got hosed, Timmy.

06:35.528 --> 06:36.628
Oh, wait a minute.

06:37.163 --> 06:37.996
What is it?

06:41.768 --> 06:42.834
Uh, I don't know.

06:44.504 --> 06:45.837
(METAL CLANKING)

06:52.678 --> 06:53.645
(CLANKING CONTINUES)

07:09.896 --> 07:10.896
