(SCREAMS)

07:36.522 --> 07:37.656
See? It's just
a scary movie.

07:38.090 --> 07:39.057
Let's watch it.

07:44.598 --> 07:48.767
<i>Wait for the gate agent</i>
<i>to give your</i>
<i>boarding announcement.</i>

07:48.769 --> 07:49.634
<i>Check your monitors.</i>
<i>Thank you kindly.</i>

07:58.478 --> 08:00.812
Fine, but if it
gets out of control,
I'm turning it off.

08:00.814 --> 08:01.646
Yeah, yeah.

