08:36.048 --> 08:37.582
(CLEARS THROAT)

08:37.583 --> 08:38.850
Um, girl...

08:40.019 --> 08:41.653
Do you know what time
the train comes?

08:42.889 --> 08:44.823
Uh, it should be about
10 minutes or so.

08:47.193 --> 08:49.861
(CHUCKLES)
Uh, do you have
a cigarette?

08:51.097 --> 08:51.997
No, sorry.

08:55.268 --> 08:56.301
Yeah, thanks.

08:58.004 --> 09:00.071
Well, happy Halloween.

09:00.073 --> 09:01.773
(SCOFFS) Come on, let's go.
I need a fucking cigarette.

09:03.543 --> 09:04.309
Come on.

09:05.645 --> 09:06.611
(LAUGHS)

09:29.937 --> 09:33.305
<i>Please stand by</i>
<i>for further information.</i>

09:54.627 --> 09:55.794
(RUSTLING)

10:08.007 --> 10:09.074
(HONKS)

10:13.946 --> 10:14.779
Please stop.

11:06.732 --> 11:07.732
(SCREAMS)

11:16.442 --> 11:18.076
What are you doing?

11:18.078 --> 11:19.277
Let me go. Help!

11:21.814 --> 11:22.781
Help!

11:24.050 --> 11:25.016
(SCREAMS)

11:33.125 --> 11:34.826
(BREATHING HEAVILY)
