help me, please!

12:42.862 --> 12:44.262
Somebody answer me!

12:46.966 --> 12:49.000
Please! (CRIES)

12:52.905 --> 12:53.972
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

12:55.908 --> 12:56.775
Who's there?

13:06.118 --> 13:07.852
Where am I?

13:07.854 --> 13:08.520
What's happening?

13:12.124 --> 13:13.424
Would someone
talk to me?

13:13.426 --> 13:14.793
Please stop screaming.

13:16.362 --> 13:18.429
What's happening to us?
This is where he keeps us.

13:19.799 --> 13:22.500
There were three of us.
There was another girl.

13:24.470 --> 13:26.237
What happened to her?

13:26.239 --> 13:28.173
She was dragged down
into that tunnel.

13:28.175 --> 13:29.908
They're pulling us down
by our chains one at a time.

13:32.878 --> 13:35.079
Why are you two
just sitting there?

13:35.081 --> 13:36.815
Why aren't you
trying to escape?

13:36.817 --> 13:38.550
