there's no way out.

13:41.253 --> 13:43.288
(RETCHING)

13:47.126 --> 13:48.159
(SOBBING)

13:51.096 --> 13:52.063
(COUGHS)

13:57.036 --> 13:58.303
Why is he keeping us here?

14:00.606 --> 14:02.607
Why doesn't he just
kill us already?

14:10.316 --> 14:11.516
Why are you
doing this?

14:12.852 --> 14:15.320
Let us go! Please!

14:15.322 --> 14:17.021
(WOMAN MAKING
ANNOUNCEMENTS ON PA)

14:35.341 --> 14:36.374
Don't cry.

14:41.513 --> 14:42.614
We're gonna die
down here.

14:44.483 --> 14:45.516
Don't say that.

14:47.653 --> 14:49.087
We're gonna get
out of here.

14:52.024 --> 14:53.491
I don't wanna die.

14:53.493 --> 14:56.394
Shut up! Just shut up!
SARA: Kristen!

14:56.396 --> 14:59.530
I can't take it anymore.
I can't keep listening
to this.

14:59.532 --> 15:03.301
She's just scared. Okay?

15:03.303 --> 15:04.602
I'm sorry.
SARA: We all are.

15:04.604 --> 15:05.937
I'm sorry.

15:08.407 --> 15:10.108
We can't fall apart
on each other now.

15:11.944 --> 15:12.977
We're all we've got.

15:17.983 --> 15:18.983
What's your name?

15:20.352 --> 15:21.386
Casey.

15:23.455 --> 15:24.555
I'm Sara.

15:26.091 --> 15:27.258
That's Kristen.

15:32.564 --> 15:33.665
There has to be
a way out of here.

15:35.200 --> 15:36.601
I told you,
there isn't.

15:39.405 --> 15:41.439
Then we have to go
down into that tunnel.

15:41.441 --> 15:44.042
What?
We can't just stay here.

15:44.044 --> 15:46.377
Going into that
tunnel is suicide.

15:46.379 --> 15:48.546
Oh, and staying
here isn't?

15:48.548 --> 15:51.616
What do you know?
You didn't see what
happened to that girl.

15:51.618 --> 15:54.986
We did. We watched her
getting dragged down
into that tunnel

15:54.988 --> 15:57.155
and she was screaming
for her life,

15:57.157 --> 15:59.524
and we were trying
to hold on to her

15:59.526 --> 16:02.260
but he just... He pulled her
right out of her hands.

16:02.262 --> 16:03.528
We're not strong enough.

16:05.631 --> 16:07.999
There's three of us now.

16:08.001 --> 16:10.535
If we go together,
we might have a chance.

16:10.537 --> 16:12.303
We don't even know
how many of them
are down there.

16:13.439 --> 16:16.007
What do you suppose we do?

16:16.009 --> 16:19.310
The only thing
we can do is
just wait here

16:19.312 --> 16:21.212
and hope that
somebody finds us.

16:23.382 --> 16:24.582
She's right, Kristen.

16:26.385 --> 16:27.452
There's no other way.

16:28.420 --> 16:30.688
No, Sara. Please.

16:30.690 --> 16:32.056
You know I'm right.

16:33.258 --> 16:35.593
Don't listen to her.
She's dead already.

16:36.061 --> 16:37.328
Don't go!

16:38.630 --> 16:39.764
I'm sorry.

16:40.733 --> 16:42.000
There's no other choice.

16:42.002 --> 16:44.068
Don't leave me here alone!

16:44.070 --> 16:46.170
He's gonna kill you.

16:46.172 --> 16:47.605
Kristen, we have to,
we can't just wait here
to see who's gonna be...

16:48.741 --> 16:50.241
(ALL SCREAMING)

16:57.516 --> 16:58.783
(SOBS)

17:01.186 --> 17:02.053
(GROWLING)

17:06.724 --> 17:07.759
Oh, my God.
It's got her.

17:07.761 --> 17:09.660
Oh, my God.

17:09.662 --> 17:12.630
Listen to me, Kristen,
we have to go now.

17:12.632 --> 17:14.098
You hear me?
We have to go down there.

17:15.034 --> 17:17.035
I can't,
I'm too scared.

17:17.037 --> 17:19.270
I know you are
and so am I,

17:19.271 --> 17:21.472
but right now
I'm thinking
about my family.

17:21.473 --> 17:23.374
I'm gonna get out of here
and I'm gonna see them again

17:23.376 --> 17:25.242
and everything's gonna be
like it was before.

17:25.244 --> 17:27.377
I know you feel the same,

17:27.380 --> 17:30.081
but we're never gonna see
them again if we don't try
to get out of here.

17:32.217 --> 17:33.785
I can't stay here
anymore, Kristen.

17:36.388 --> 17:37.522
I can't wait
here to die.

17:40.159 --> 17:41.459
I just can't.

17:44.129 --> 17:46.264
We're gonna make it.
Do you understand me?

17:47.366 --> 17:49.233
We're gonna
be all right.

17:49.235 --> 17:52.336
Just stay close
and be quiet.

18:06.085 --> 18:07.285
(CHAINS CLANKING)

18:31.710 --> 18:33.411
This is where it ends.
Right, stay here.

18:43.689 --> 18:45.456
(GRUNTS)

18:45.458 --> 18:47.125
Oh, God, look, look, look!
Use it on the chains.

18:50.896 --> 18:52.196
I think it's big enough.

18:53.832 --> 18:54.866
(CHAIN CLANKING)

18:55.667 --> 18:56.834
I think it's working.

19:04.576 --> 19:05.476
(SCREAMS)

19:06.311 --> 19:07.211
(SCREAMING)

19:08.847 --> 19:09.714
(SOBBING)

19:11.383 --> 19:12.316
(GROWLS)

19:16.488 --> 19:17.355
(SCREAMING)

19:19.191 --> 19:19.891
(SCREAMS)

19:25.631 --> 19:26.564
Oh, God!

19:27.533 --> 19:28.533
(SCREAMING)

19:29.768 --> 19:30.635
(SQUELCHING)

19:41.413 --> 19:42.313
(SCREAMS)

19:52.357 --> 19:53.291
(WHIMPERING)

20:12.344 --> 20:14.845
Help me,
help me please.

20:14.847 --> 20:16.847
There's something down there.
We have to get out of here.

20:19.384 --> 20:20.351
Come on!

20:33.865 --> 20:34.832
(SCREAMS)

20:36.802 --> 20:38.302
(CASEY SCREAMING)

20:44.576 --> 20:45.810
(WHIMPERING)

21:10.736 --> 21:11.869
