21:37.562 --> 21:38.496
(HISSING)

21:43.769 --> 21:44.735
No!

21:45.771 --> 21:46.637
WOMAN: Please.

21:58.450 --> 21:59.317
Please.

22:00.385 --> 22:01.552
Please stop.

22:02.487 --> 22:03.387
Please stop.

22:13.498 --> 22:14.498
Don't hurt my baby.

22:15.801 --> 22:16.701
(WHIMPERING)

22:19.071 --> 22:20.004
(SCREAMS)

22:20.806 --> 22:21.672
(SCREAMING)

22:29.081 --> 22:30.648
(SCREAMING)

23:24.703 --> 23:25.903
(CASEY CRYING)

23:32.711 --> 23:33.677
(SOBBING)

24:02.107 --> 24:03.040
(HONKS)

24:05.143 --> 24:07.011
That was sick!

24:07.013 --> 24:09.513
Okay, that is enough
for tonight.

24:09.515 --> 24:10.748
TIMMY: Hey,
what're you doing?

24:10.750 --> 24:11.916
SARAH: I'm turning it off.

24:13.485 --> 24:15.119
It's too violent
for the two of you.

24:15.121 --> 24:17.054
TIMMY: No, it's not.
We've seen way worse.

24:17.056 --> 24:21.625
You're too young
to be watching a baby cut
out of someone's stomach.

24:21.627 --> 24:23.861
SARAH: Come on, let's go.
It's bedtime.
Bedtime?

24:23.863 --> 24:26.797
