Tia, go wash your face.

24:26.799 --> 24:28.799
I want the both of you
to brush your teeth.

24:28.801 --> 24:30.801
Man, it was
just getting good.
Aw.

24:30.803 --> 24:32.803
I know.
I liked the clown.

24:32.805 --> 24:34.939
Yeah, he was great.
I liked when he honked
his horn at the lady.

24:34.941 --> 24:37.508
(LAUGHS) That was so funny.

24:37.510 --> 24:40.544
Yeah, that was hysterical.

24:40.546 --> 24:41.679
I'm gonna be up
to check on you guys
in 10 minutes.

25:09.908 --> 25:11.141
(CELL PHONE VIBRATING)

25:15.214 --> 25:20.684
(CHUCKLES)
What is that
supposed to mean?

25:20.686 --> 25:26.924
It's already been
quite an eventful evening.

25:26.926 --> 25:28.692
