26:18.109 --> 26:19.076
Timmy!

26:20.145 --> 26:21.345
Hold on a minute, Dee.

26:23.882 --> 26:25.716
What's going on up there?

26:25.718 --> 26:28.652
TIA: Sarah,
Timmy spit in my hair!

26:28.654 --> 26:30.321
