26:45.838 --> 26:47.137
Yes, I am.

26:47.139 --> 26:48.072
Speaking...
(THUD)

26:51.643 --> 26:53.677
Speaking of good friends,

26:53.679 --> 26:54.979
do you wanna meet me
for a drink after this?

26:54.981 --> 26:57.014
<i>Yeah, I can totally do tha.</i>

26:57.016 --> 26:58.349
All right, perfect.
I need one.

26:58.351 --> 27:01.018
I'll text you
when I'm leaving.

27:01.020 --> 27:03.721
<i>Cool.</i>
<i>Oh, and Sarah...</i>
<i>Yeah?</i>

27:03.723 --> 27:04.822
<i>Don't get killed.</i>

27:04.824 --> 27:06.090
Funny.

27:06.092 --> 27:07.157
<i>Bye.</i>
<i>Bye.</i>

27:08.693 --> 27:09.660
(THUD)

27:36.054 --> 27:37.354
(GASPS)

