Where is it?

28:37.082 --> 28:37.915
Can I have it, please?

28:38.783 --> 28:40.951
(CHUCKLES) No.

28:40.953 --> 28:43.287
I don't know why you're
making such a big deal
out of this.

28:43.289 --> 28:45.189
My parents are just
gonna give it to me
in the morning.

28:45.191 --> 28:47.157
All right, then.
The faster you get
your little butt to bed

28:47.159 --> 28:48.092
the faster you'll
get your tape.

